														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-3770717">
									

<p>It's attached to SCP-023's article for purely out-of-universe reasons (to encourage WikiWalking); in-universe, the Foundation doesn't know any of this, and has no good way of finding it out without resorting to my least-favourite explanation convention: The anonymous note at the end. This dilemma bugged me for years until I decided to just write a tale instead.</p>
<p>I'll try to keep this character in mind for later things, but she's fairly limited in her scope of unique ways to affect a story that's mostly about physical things.</p>

